     90          // =============================================================================
     91          // Begin Update of TC Link Key
     92          
     93          // The TC link key may be updated on a timely basis, if desired. For instance,
     94          // if a device is joining a network where the Trust Center is pre-R21 and the
     95          // device knows that the TC will be upgraded to post-R21 at some point, the
     96          // joining device may choose to update its Trust Center link key on a timely
     97          // basis such that, eventually, the update completes successfully.
     98          // Other applications may choose to regularly update their TC link key for
     99          // security reasons.
    100          

